settings.description: This is a Level Remaked From Super Mario World, Awesome Level Dude!
Magic Blocks, are on Buster Beetle Room, also Room 4 is Bonus Room, so Enjoy!
You need to master number block swimming to beat this one. Watch out for Big Bass! Now with an E-Coin.

name: E-Coin at the end, Cheep Water

settings.description: Climb up inside a volcano and go digging for Ace Coins!  Watch out, it's hot!
Use the metal mushroom to get to the top of the temple, where you'll face off against Big Boo!
Mario's least threatening foes have come together to create insanity in the sewers.
Bullet Bills and Goombas' with shoes seem to want to ruin your day as you compete in the Green Mountain Climbing Contest.
It's all just Tetriminos in this wacky world.
In this field, Fireflowers grow naturally out of the floor, how convenient!
